  <brief_title>Active Video Games to Promote Physical Activity in Children With Cancer</brief_title>
  <official_title>Active Video Games to Promote Physical Activity, Motor Performance and Quality of Life in Children With Cancer: an Intervention Study With 2-year Follow-up</official_title>
